claim.claim-text:
1. A vibratory spiral conveyor for transporting an object, the conveyor comprising:
a first spiral deck defining a conveying surface for supporting the object and including a plurality of tier segments;
a second spiral deck operatively coupled side-by-side to the first spiral deck and defining a conveying surface for supporting the object and including a plurality of tier segments;
an exciter mass assembly including a vibration generator coupled to the first and second spiral decks for generating a vibratory force, wherein the vibratory force advances the object along the first and second spiral decks.
